name: Gundam Onami - Hero's and Villains Series
description: First in a series called "Heroes and Villains". These are the various characters that I loved and influenced me and my designs. This piece is called "Onami" after my friend who passed named Kei Onami who designed the most incredible Gundams in my college days. He passed away right before embarking on his design career, I think of him often especially when doing this and other pieces coming. I will be releasing on a bonding curve so get it early while it's more affordable.
